## Relations

Suppliers Table 
(each plant is supplied by one supplier, but a supplier can supply many plants)
One-to-many relationship

Categories Table 
(each plant belongs to one category: Medical, Industrial, Gardening, etc.)
One-to-many relationship

Purposes Table (plants can have multiple purposes: many-to-many relationship)

Plant_Purposes Table 
(junction table for many-to-many relationship between Plants and Purposes)

Many-to-Many Relationship: Plants to Purposes via Plant_Purposes.
